              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background-color: #252e33">
              <h1 data-i18n="SIGN_LANGUAGE_COURSES">Sign Language Courses</h1>
              <p data-i18n="SIGN_LANGUAGE_COURSES_DESC">
                We offer comprehensive sign language courses in Arabic, designed
